  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"2.3.1\" data-text=\"Lifecycle Version 2.3.1\" tabindex=\"-1\">Lifecycle Version 2.3.1</h3>\n<p>March 24, 2021</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.lifecycle:lifecycle-*:2.3.1</code> is released. <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/ab69093e69997058cb4a9e61203401169b6ee2a8..0b84d3ed85bf44f60f4fdda15ef20767cfe06876/lifecycle\">Version 2.3.1 contains these commits.</a></p>\n<p><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>The <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">NonNullableMutableLiveData</code> lint rule can now properly\ndifferentiate between field variables with different nullability. (<a href=\"https://issuetracker.google.com/issues/169249668\">b/169249668</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"version_230_3\" data-text=\"Version 2.3.0\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 2.3.0</h2>",
